00:00:13.220 --> 00:00:20.280
As you know, treatment of extranodal marginal zone lymphoma is not well established.

00:00:20.700 --> 00:00:26.560
There was only one randomized trial, ISLG-19, that compared rituximab to rituximab versus

00:00:26.560 --> 00:00:32.200
chlorambucil and demonstrated the combination induces better event-free survival, but there

00:00:32.200 --> 00:00:33.640
was no difference in overall survival.

00:00:34.200 --> 00:00:41.740
