00:01:42.720 --> 00:01:47.580
mozentuximab for eight cycles with restaging after a fourth cycle.

00:01:47.580 --> 00:01:53.340
The goal of this study is to enroll 35 patients, and the primary endpoint is complete response

00:01:53.340 --> 00:01:56.280
